00:45:45.650 --> 00:45:48.920 align:middle line:84%
Tell me about this awakening
the species within.

00:45:48.920 --> 00:45:52.670 align:middle line:84%
>>HUBBARD: Well, I'm doing a
wonderful intensive for a year.

00:45:52.670 --> 00:45:54.050 align:middle line:90%
It's 52 weeks.

00:45:54.050 --> 00:45:56.630 align:middle line:84%
And each week, I
have a code that

00:45:56.630 --> 00:45:59.300 align:middle line:84%
came from what I call
my "universal self."

00:45:59.300 --> 00:46:01.430 align:middle line:84%
Now, my universal
self-- or yours,

00:46:01.430 --> 00:46:05.360 align:middle line:84%
or anyone's-- is
yourself in the future.

00:46:05.360 --> 00:46:08.360 align:middle line:84%
And it comes in
as who you are now

00:46:08.360 --> 00:46:11.780 align:middle line:84%
when you put your attention
on your deep and radical

00:46:11.780 --> 00:46:13.070 align:middle line:90%
potential.

00:46:13.070 --> 00:46:16.460 align:middle line:84%
So your universal
self is encoded

00:46:16.460 --> 00:46:18.075 align:middle line:90%
with what you are becoming.

00:46:18.075 --> 00:46:20.480 align:middle line:84%
And in Awaken the
New Species, we

00:46:20.480 --> 00:46:23.360 align:middle line:84%
put attention on
what we are becoming.

00:46:23.360 --> 00:46:24.350 align:middle line:90%
And it comes in.

00:46:24.350 --> 00:46:27.890 align:middle line:84%
And then we share it
with the inspired writing

00:46:27.890 --> 00:46:32.360 align:middle line:84%
and with the codes and with
very well-known speakers.

00:46:32.360 --> 00:46:34.100 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This is
a great idea when

00:46:34.100 --> 00:46:35.720 align:middle line:84%
