00:46:38.510 --> 00:46:41.791 align:middle line:84%
That is a fantastic
creative visioning process.

00:46:41.791 --> 00:46:42.790 align:middle line:90%
>>HUBBARD: It's so good.

00:46:42.790 --> 00:46:46.430 align:middle line:84%
