sapiens, looking

00:46:57.260 --> 00:46:59.070 align:middle line:90%
at my full potential self.

00:46:59.070 --> 00:47:01.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's amazing.

00:47:01.030 --> 00:47:03.920 align:middle line:84%
>>HUBBARD: The full
potential self coming closer

00:47:03.920 --> 00:47:06.150 align:middle line:90%
and going like this.

00:47:06.150 --> 00:47:09.380 align:middle line:84%
So the crossing
over is the feeling

00:47:09.380 --> 00:47:11.690 align:middle line:84%
that whatever that
is inside you that

00:47:11.690 --> 00:47:16.880 align:middle line:84%
is your deep social and
spiritual potentiality

00:47:16.880 --> 00:47:19.590 align:middle line:90%
has incarnated as you.

00:47:19.590 --> 00:47:23.010 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So who is that universal
