00:47:23.810 --> 00:47:24.890 align:middle line:90%
>>HUBBARD: She's here now.

00:47:24.890 --> 00:47:25.848 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: She's here now.

00:47:25.848 --> 00:47:27.099 align:middle line:90%
What is she doing?

00:47:27.099 --> 00:47:29.390 align:middle line:84%
>>HUBBARD: Well, she is going
to awaken as many species

00:47:29.390 --> 00:47:31.010 align:middle line:90%
as she can.

00:47:31.010 --> 00:47:34.940 align:middle line:84%
