of evolution is a sacred story.

00:47:45.860 --> 00:47:47.450 align:middle line:84%
And we have all the
biblical stories

00:47:47.450 --> 00:47:52.010 align:middle line:84%
and all the stories of so many
great avatars and cultures.

00:47:52.010 --> 00:47:55.430 align:middle line:84%
We all have one
single, great story--

00:47:55.430 --> 00:47:59.750 align:middle line:84%
is that from nothing at all has
been created everything that is

00:47:59.750 --> 00:48:04.730 align:middle line:84%
and that we are participants
in that creation.

00:48:04.730 --> 00:48:07.340 align:middle line:84%
The goal in the
early Christianity

00:48:07.340 --> 00:48:09.200 align:middle line:90%
