00:48:09.200 --> 00:48:10.820 align:middle line:90%
What's our goal?

00:48:10.820 --> 00:48:13.755 align:middle line:84%
You could say is that first
full coming of humanity.

00:48:13.755 --> 00:48:15.130 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Right,
the Christ within.

00:48:15.130 --> 00:48:15.930 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:48:15.930 --> 00:48:17.780 align:middle line:84%
>>HUBBARD: Christ
within and socially

00:48:17.780 --> 00:48:22.250 align:middle line:84%
and politically and economically
and environmentally.

00:48:22.250 --> 00:48:28.460 align:middle line:84%
So for me, the women awakening
the world, the Church

00:48:28.460 --> 00:48:32.630 align:middle line:84%
of Evolutionary Love, the
Awaken the New Species,

00:48:32.630 --> 00:48:35.180 align:middle line:84%
the kinds of thing
like you do on your--

00:48:35.180 --> 00:48:38.150 align:middle line:84%
