be placed together.

00:48:38.150 --> 00:48:40.730 align:middle line:84%
And we need to have a
collective experience

00:48:40.730 --> 00:48:41.990 align:middle line:90%
of our own greatness.

00:48:41.990 --> 00:48:44.660 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Essentially, it's
like creating a new religion

00:48:44.660 --> 00:48:46.205 align:middle line:90%
