00:49:52.984 --> 00:49:54.020 align:middle line:90%
There's--

00:49:54.020 --> 00:49:54.360 align:middle line:90%
>>HUBBARD: Yeah.

00:49:54.360 --> 00:49:56.990 align:middle line:84%
