00:50:31.220 --> 00:50:32.720 align:middle line:84%
And you are most
definitely invited.

00:50:32.720 --> 00:50:34.030 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Well, thank you.

00:50:34.030 --> 00:50:34.830 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:50:34.830 --> 00:50:35.790 align:middle line:90%
I mean, I love this.

00:50:35.790 --> 00:50:36.748 align:middle line:90%
>>HUBBARD: In November.

00:50:36.748 --> 00:50:40.010 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's all working
towards the collective whole.

00:50:40.010 --> 00:50:42.980 align:middle line:84%
And it would bring a community
together-- not that that's

00:50:42.980 --> 00:50:43.977 align:middle line:90%
